text: Angk Prasat Commune () is a khum (commune) in Kiri Vong District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, Angk Prasat Commune has 10 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable mw-collapsible" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21040101 |Pou Ta Mok |ពោធិ៍តាម៉ុក |- !2 |21040102 |Roneam Tnaot |រនាមត្នោត |- !3 |21040103 |Prachreay |ប្រជ្រាយ |- !4 |21040104 |Angk Prasat |អង្គប្រាសាទ |- !5 |21040105 |Phngeas |ភ្ងាស |- !6 |21040106 |Voat Svay |វត្ដស្វាយ |- !7 |21040107 |Phnum Lonteah |ភ្នំលន្ទះ |- !8 |21040108 |Tuol Svay |ទួលស្វាយ |- !9 |21040109 |Svay Thum |ស្វាយធំ |- !10 |21040110 |Krabak |ក្របាក់ |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Kiri Vong District
